{"lemma":"غِبُّ","slug":"غِبُّ","root":"غ.ب.ب","root_slug":"غ-ب-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ب-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","prep","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31314","n31315"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to come on alternate days upon"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"vulgar form of عَبَّ (ʕabba, “to gulp”)","tags":["form-of","vulgar"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَبَّ (ḡabba) (form I), visit per interval, arrival in an alternating fashion","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"],"examples":[{"text":"حُمَّى الْغِبّ","english":"tertian fever"},{"text":"ثُمَّ يُسْقَى غِبًّا يُسْقَى يَوْمًا وَيُتْرَكُ يَوْمًا","english":"Then one irrigates alternatingly, one irrigates one day and desists from it the other."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"end, outcome, fine, result, output","examples":[{"text":"ولقد ظهرت واتضحت نتائج سوء التربية، وحصد الذين أهملوا في السابق غِبَّ هذا الإهمال، كما شاهد الجميع آثار ذلك على بعض الشباب.","english":"The results of bad upbringing became patent, and he who has been heedless in the past reaped the output of heedlessness, like everyone witnesses its spoors on a deal of the youth."}]},{"pos":"prep","gloss":"after, following in time"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"depressed terrain"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bosom of the sea, gulf","tags":["Yemen"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31314","headword_ar":"غُبٌّ","root":"gb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sea dashing so that it goes far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"runs, upon the land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gub~aAnN","text_ar":"غُبَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Depressed land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agobaAbN","text_ar":"اَغْبَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gubuwbN","text_ar":"غُبُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gub~aAnN","text_ar":"غُبَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31315","headword_ar":"غِبٌّ","root":"gb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[a subst., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zimo'N","text_ar":"ظِمْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A coming"},{"kind":"text","text":"(of camels, S, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to water on alternate days; coming to the water one day and not the next day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being kept from it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day and two nights:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturing one day and coming to the water the next day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and this is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gib~","text_ar":"غِبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the ass. (TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirodu Algib~i","text_ar":"وِرْدُ الغِبِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The coming"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the water in the second of two nights"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as is shown by the context of a passage in which it occurs in the S and O and K voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalaqN","text_ar":"طَلَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the second of two days."},{"kind":"text","text":"] But the saying of a rájiz,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"waHum~araAtN $urobuhun~a gib~u"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And hummarahs"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a species of birds]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose drinking is every hour"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"every little while"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~a","text_ar":"كُلَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAEapK","text_ar":"سَاعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (S, O.) ―         -b2-  Also [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sayoru gib~K","text_ar":"سَيْرُ غِبٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A journey of two days"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof one is without any watering of the camels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the case of which they are watered only on the first and third of three days"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nbj","text_ar":"نبج"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A visiting once in every week:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) so says El-Hasan: (S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at intervals of some days: after some days:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, IAth: [see also its verb:]) from the same word used in relation to camels. (IAth.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuro gib~FA tazodado Hub~FA","text_ar":"زُرْ غِبًّا تَزْدَدْ حُبًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or, accord. to common usage,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hib~FA","text_ar":"حِبًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":", to assimilate it to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gib~FA","text_ar":"غِبًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Visit once a week,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at intervals of some days;"},{"kind":"text","text":"not frequently, or not every day: so"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thou shalt have more love:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a prov., respecting which see Freytag's Arab. Prov. i. 587; where"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gub~FA","text_ar":"غُبًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gib~FA","text_ar":"غِبًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) [See another ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraj~ala","text_ar":"تَرَجَّلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence.] The saying of Zeyd-el-Fawáris"},{"kind":"quote","text":"yaraAniY AlEaduw~u baEoda gib~i liqaAy^ihi"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The enemy will see me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the day of meeting with him by a day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 732.) ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attacking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a fever"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one day and intermitting one day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the same word used in relation to camels. (S, O, Msb.) ―         -b5-  And A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tertian"},{"kind":"text","text":"fever;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that attacks one day and intermits one day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hum~aY gib~N","text_ar":"حُمَّى غِبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tertian fever"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; using it as an epithet: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hum~aY Algib~i","text_ar":"حُمَّى الغِبِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlv","text_ar":"ثلث"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"end; conclusion; latter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state; issue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAqibapN","text_ar":"عَاقِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, MA, O, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=xirN","text_ar":"ا=خِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, * O, * TA;) of an affair, (S, A, O, Msb,) of any kind, (S, O,) or of a thing; (K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magab~apN","text_ar":"مَغَبَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, O, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migab~N","text_ar":"مِغَبٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MA.) And [hence]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gib~a","text_ar":"غِبَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"After;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoda","text_ar":"بَعْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": thus in the phrases"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gib~a AlA^a*aAni","text_ar":"غِبَّ الاَذَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"After the call to prayer"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gib~a Als~alaAmi","text_ar":"غِبَّ السَّلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"After salutation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the salutation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and one says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"gib~a AlS~abaAHi yaHomadu Alqawomu Als~uraY"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"After daybreak, the party commend nightjourneying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but more commonly,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einoda AlS~abaAHi","text_ar":"عِنْدَ الصَّبَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"srY","text_ar":"سرى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='N gib~N","text_ar":"مَا=ءٌ غِبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Distant water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyaAhN A^agobaAbN","text_ar":"مِيَاهٌ اَغْبَابٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distant waters."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","A","MA","Msb"]}]}}